"""
This notebook calculates Value at Risk (VaR) and Conditional Value at Risk (CVaR)
from model predictions. These are standard risk metrics used in finance:
- VaR: Maximum expected loss at a given confidence level
- CVaR: Expected loss beyond VaR (tail risk)
"""

